Package: WPD
Title: World Panel Data: A Macroeconomic Data Visualization and Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.0.43
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin", "Peeters", , "benjaminpeeters@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5095-2021"))
Description: A panel-data package providing access to global economic and
    social indicators. The package includes a large database (approximately 50MB)
    of world panel data that is loaded on demand through the 'wp_data' function.
    Features include customizable time series plots, cross-sectional analysis
    tools, scatter plots with trend analysis, bar charts for comparative analysis,
    built-in seasonal adjustment capabilities, and support for both annual and
    quarterly frequencies. The package focuses on macroeconomic indicators
    including GDP, trade, prices, employment, and financial data across multiple
    countries and regions.
SystemRequirements: At least 100MB disk space for installation.
